    • generateBass

      public List<Part> generateBass(int lower, int upper, int key, boolean random, int intype, int inbeats, int restChance, int modFrequency)
      Generates the music for a bass guitar
      Parameters:
      lower - bottom left hand corner of fretboard to work with
      upper - upper right hand corner of fretboard to work with
      key - key to work with
      random - if false it is all the selected key, if true it modulates every so often
      intype - type of beat in time signature
      inbeats - number of beats in time signature
      restChance - chance of a note being a rest, 1/restChance
      modFrequency - how many measures between key modulation, if random is true
      Returns:
      Part list
